pandangannya agak aneh?

170
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:19,480
Adakah?

171
00:17:19,680 --> 00:17:21,349
Seperti sangat dekat denganmu.

172
00:17:23,069 --> 00:17:24,640
Sepertinya kau salah lihat.

173
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:29,480
Sepertinya aku memang salah.

174
00:17:31,360 --> 00:17:31,800
Aku pergi.

175
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:33,240
Hati-hati di jalan, sampai jumpa.

176
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:33,960
